      <sentence n="1">
        <kanji>天皇我御命爾坐世</kanji>
        <transcription>sumyera ga opo mikoto ni ma se</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="2">
        <kanji>久度古關二所乃</kanji>
        <transcription>kudo puruseki puta tokoro no</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="3">
        <kanji>宮爾弖仕奉來留</kanji>
        <transcription>miya ni site tukape maturi kitar eru</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="4">
        <kanji>皇御神乃廣前爾白給久</kanji>
        <transcription>sumye mi kamwi no piro mapye ni mawosi tamapa ku</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="5">
        <kanji>皇御神乃乞比給万比之</kanji>
        <transcription>sumye mi kamwi no ko pi ta mapi si</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="6">
        <kanji>任爾</kanji>
        <transcription>manima ni</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="7">
        <kanji>此所乃底津石根爾宮柱廣敷立</kanji>
        <transcription>ko no tokoro no soko tu ipa ne ni miya basira piro siki tate</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="8">
        <kanji>高天乃原爾千木高知弖</kanji>
        <transcription>taka ma no para ni ti gwi taka siri te</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="9">
        <kanji>天乃御蔭日乃御蔭止定奉弖</kanji>
        <transcription>ame no mi kage pi no mi kage to sadame maturi te</transcription>
      </sentence>
