      </sentence>
      <sentence n="17">
        <kanji>四方國乃進禮留</kanji>
        <transcription>yo mo no kuni no tate matur eru</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="18">
        <kanji>御調乃荷前乎取竝弖</kanji>
        <transcription>mi tukwi no nozaki wo tori narabe te</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="19">
        <kanji>御酒波𤭖乃門〈閇〉高知</kanji>
        <transcription>mi ki pa mika no pe taka siri</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="20">
        <kanji>𤭖乃腹滿竝弖</kanji>
        <transcription>mika no para mite narabe te</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="21">
        <kanji>山野物波甘菜辛菜</kanji>
