      </sentence>
      <sentence n="22">
        <kanji>靑海原乃物波鰭乃廣物鰭狹物息都毛波邊都毛波爾至末弖雜</kanji>
        <transcription>awo mi no para no mono pa pata no piro mono pata no sa mono oki tu mo pa pye tu mo pa ni itaru made kusagusa no</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="23">
        <kanji>物乎如橫山置高成弖</kanji>
